{"tid":1485751,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁振英撰文質疑浸大生英文唔好 反俾學生指出文中錯字","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T05:29:29.000Z","uid":63183,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4f7dc95b9d2954731ad5cc2271a1523717c08c10","tid":1485751,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:35:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/3040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F3040&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=7d30ad7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/3040</a><br />\n退伍特首梁振英今晚忽然喺Facebook貼文攻擊浸大學生會會長方仲賢的英語水平「太恐怖」，揚言請錢大康校長向納稅人回應及公開浸大學生入學成績。不過，梁振英對方仲賢英文嘅指控欠缺證據，反而馬上俾浸大學生指出其錯字。中文水平差劣至極。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Leungspeech.png?w=503&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2FLeungspeech.png%3Fw%3D503%26ssl%3D1&h=9fff856d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n梁振英稱「方同學攪學生會活動，去鴨寮街買10支雷射槍，不如專心學習，首先要惡補英文。」此句已將「搞活動」嘅「搞」錯寫成「攪」。中文學者朱承樸指出，「搞」的意義大體上和「做、弄、幹、辦 」等動詞相近，有策劃、設計、用心思、動腦筋等含義；攪就只有「擾亂」同「混和」之義。[1] 研究指多數港人都係寫「搞活動」居多，梁振英中文仲差過普通市民。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英指責方仲賢購買「雷射槍」。然而「雷射槍」專指激光武器，方仲賢當日喺鴨寮街所買嘅僅僅係觀星用嘅雷射筆。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，梁振英在任特首期間經常講錯字，誤導廣大市民。佢曾經話對於拉布「深痛惡絕」。正確講法係出自《孟子》嘅「深惡痛絕」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/gongjyuhok.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/leungeng.jpg?w=670&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2Fleungeng.jpg%3Fw%3D670%26ssl%3D1&h=a4b6972f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，梁振英自己嘅英文水平都令人不敢恭維。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英喺籌備參選特首時也曾承認，當年中五會考時失手，不獲英皇書院原校收錄，只能就讀香港工業學院測量系高級文憑課程。<br />\n<br />\n（按：筆者亦不妨公開下點考入浸大：中文5** [相當於A-level A]）"},{"pid":"b877c4e3d9b0a4cbb53269b421898c4f9d577bb5","tid":1485751,"uid":49018,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:37:13.000Z","msg":"Three C meeting<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c7d824edd5172adda1f38063724e6e31e62de2","tid":1485751,"uid":4288,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b877c4e3d9b0a4cbb53269b421898c4f9d577bb5","tid":1485751,"uid":49018,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:37:13.000Z","msg":"Three C meeting<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"我都諗起呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92560501c5bdde5272fbfc04137acaca722574a6","tid":1485751,"uid":260367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"6a936ad0646eb2bc66a5ad370af9123b0720a1a1","tid":1485751,"uid":115579,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:42:26.000Z","msg":"英文又唔得 中文又唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做生意做到零 全部人都圍屌 到底呢件野點上位"},{"pid":"299507fa3dafb1ce280ccc691c5fcadc8c361a23","tid":1485751,"uid":75647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a1e6ee914c444feaed693e8bbb8cd5da268f61","tid":1485751,"uid":49018,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6a936ad0646eb2bc66a5ad370af9123b0720a1a1","tid":1485751,"uid":115579,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:42:26.000Z","msg":"英文又唔得 中文又唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做生意做到零 全部人都圍屌 到底呢件野點上位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:46:50.000Z","msg":"唐英年戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d36b80e7a6064d85b429d3cdebaf1b4f8a8003","tid":1485751,"uid":27558