e":{"pid":"6a936ad0646eb2bc66a5ad370af9123b0720a1a1","tid":1485751,"uid":115579,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:42:26.000Z","msg":"英文又唔得 中文又唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做生意做到零 全部人都圍屌 到底呢件野點上位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:13:18.000Z","msg":"所以咪成世人靠ugl呢啲方法去揾食囉⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685ed3a8e8e4bd4ed03b5a11605819e93207edfc","tid":1485751,"uid":38761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:24:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其實梁主席說「... 英文水平太恐怖了...」是要諷刺身為一國之君的習主席的英文水平，甚至去到連英文字母有30個也不知道的境地。令14億中國人在G20的各國領袖面前出醜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=466533\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D466533&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=c2479ec4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D466533&h=560609d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=466533</a><br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"12e2933b160d39981b6cedf9ae5ae2493b3a27c1","tid":1485751,"uid":39492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廢老就係咁, 係要衝出嚟柒兩鑊先心息"}]}